# Wordcloud Submission App

A lightweight Streamlit web app for collecting short responses and visualizing them in a live wordcloud.

## ðŸ’¡ Features
- Clean QR-scannable form for user submissions (2 words/phrases)
- Submissions saved with timestamps to a CSV file
- Dynamic "Thank You" page with emoji and QR code sharing
- Ready for deployment on [Render](https://render.com)

